《'''兩個大溪地女人'''》是[[保羅·高更|保羅·高更]]在1899年繪製的一副布面油畫，描繪的是兩名上身赤裸的[[大溪地|大溪地]]女性。這幅畫在1949年由[[威廉·丘奇·奧斯本|威廉·丘奇·奧斯本]]捐給[[大都會藝術博物館|大都會藝術博物館]]，現時是該博物館的永久藏品。<ref name="Metropolitan Museum of Art">[http://www.metmuseum.org/Collections/search-the-collections/110000888?rpp=20&pg=1&ft=two+tahitian+women&pos=2 Two Tahitian Women] - Metropolitan Museum of Art Retrieved 2012-07-15</ref>  

畫中一人抱臂，一人捧著芒果花。與馬奈的《[[草地上的午餐|草地上的午餐]]》或《[[奧林匹亞_(馬奈)|奧林匹亞]]》一樣，這幅畫遵循將花或果實與女性乳房相對比的藝術傳統。<ref>{{Cite book |last=Sturma |first=Michael |authorlink= |title=South Sea Maidens: Western Fantasy and Sexual Politics in the South Pacific |publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group |year=2002 |location= |pages=88–90 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Ttl3FT0UqngC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false |isbn=0-313-31674-0}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |last=Schwarz |first=Daniel R. |authorlink=Daniel R. Schwarz |title=Reconfiguring Modernism: Explorations in the Relationship Between Modern Art and Modern Literature |publisher=St. Matin's Press |year=1997 |location=New York | pages=85–86 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=xy-9YuYTLhkC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false |isbn=0-312-12660-3}}</ref>兩名模特還在高更的另外兩幅作品《Faa Iheihe》（1898）和《Rupe, Rupe》（1899）中出現。<ref name="Metropolitan Museum of Art"/>

此画在2011年4月1日於[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]的[[國家藝廊|國家藝廊]]參展時遭到蓄意破坏，一名叫做蘇珊·伯恩斯（Susan Burns）的女性突然對此畫的樹脂封面予以重擊，但並沒能傷害到畫作本身。該婦女後被收押，博物館方面以財產破壞和盜竊罪發起起訴。<ref>{{cite news | title = National Gallery visitor attacks Gauguin painting, officials say | date = 2011-04-04 | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/national-gallery-visitor-attacks-gauguin-painting-officials-say/2011/04/03/AFoATUXC_story.html?hpid=z4 | work = Washington Post | accessdate = 2011-04-05 | archive-date = 2011-08-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110831030802/http://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/national-gallery-visitor-attacks-gauguin-painting-officials-say/2011/04/03/AFoATUXC_story.html?hpid=z4 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-12966698| title=Gauguin painting in Washington DC attacked by woman| work=BBC news| date=5 April 2011| accessdate=2014-12-12| archive-date=2015-04-14| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414123412/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-12966698| dead-url=no}}</ref>

